This baseline wraps the published Nimbus inference library and applies it
to the DeepCell Types evaluation harness.

Nimbus is described in:

  J. L. Rumberger et al., "Nimbus: A deep learning approach for cell
  segmentation and marker quantification in multiplexed tissue imaging",
  Nature Methods (2025).

The Nimbus library (``nimbus-inference``) is distributed separately on
PyPI; consult that project for its license terms.


